1 zw/w foto van het geheel. Notitie FG: 'Sale "Property of a Gentleman", Christie's, April 1, 1960, 38..Gns. Hallsborough. PIETER BRUEGHEL THE ELDER. 105 A Wedding Feast. Peasants are dancing to the music of two bagpipers while the bridegroom talks to a group of women on the left [...] On panel, 14 in. by 21in. See Plate LVI; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. Jan Brueghel, pasticcio from various Bruegel motifs the landscape taken from the Beekeepers (Berlin). Against P.B.I not only pasticcio character as such, but the lacking connexion betw. the landscape and the long procession parallel to picture plane of the foreground figures.
